    <abstract>
      <t>   This document proposes to use Source Prefix Advertisement (SPA)
   messages for advertising hidden source prefixes and discovering the
   hidden paths of source prefixes.  The accuracy of existing inter-
   domain SAV mechanisms like EFP-uRPF can be improved by SPA.

	 </t>
